        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"161199\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Same question: I would sometims like to put pictures I already have in whatsapp or whatever\u2026 but have no clue how to do it.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>If it\u2019s saved on your drive, go to Full Editor, scroll down to Attachments, click and follow directions there - it\u2019s pretty much the same as uploading a file anywhere on a website.</p>\n<p>If you have it on a website somewhere, you can use the image or media insert buttons above the text box on your post.  Hover over the icons and they\u2019ll tell you what they are - to the right of the Bold and Italic etc.  Then paste the URL in the middle as shown.</p>",
